These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
There 2 different types of food: blueberry, corn
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: d&b, dubstep
There are 2 different nationalities: spanish, egyptian
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: august, december
1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the egyptian##3
2. the person eating corn is in an even position##4
3. the fan of dubstep is the person eating blueberry##1
4. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Food      | blueberry  | corn   |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep     | d&b   |
| Nationality         | egyptian | spanish |
| Birthday     | august | december    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: fanta, water
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: pop, jazz
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, alhambra
The people have 2 different hobbies: gardening, baking
1. the alhambra-smoker is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of pop is the person who's hobby is baking##1
3. the person drinking water is on the right of the fan of jazz##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Beverage          | fanta     | water |
| Music-Genre   | jazz | pop  |
| Cigar           | alhambra         | cain     |
| Hobby     | gardening   | baking    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: july, september
2 different games are played: monopoly, backgammon
There 2 different types of food: cherry, grapefruit
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, swisher
1. the swisher-smoker is on the left or right of the person playing backgammon##3
2. the person eating grapefruit is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
3. the person who's birthday is in july is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Birthday    | september     | july |
| Game         | backgammon | monopoly    |
| Food         | cherry         | grapefruit        |
| Cigar   | davidoff         | swisher    |

