.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-4::.
There are 2 different nationalities: malaysian, british
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skateboarding, ice-hockey
There are 2 different favourite colors: coral, light-blue
City: miami, london
1. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the person who likes coral##1
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the malaysian##1
3. the person traveling to london is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Nationality      | british     | malaysian |
| Sport          | ice-hockey   | skateboarding  |
| Color         | coral | light-blue     |
| City   | miami  | london         |

