.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-20::.
City: paris, liverpool
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, fonseca
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: bellflower, balloon-flower
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: spy, zombie
1. the fonseca-smoker is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
2. the person who growsbellflower is on the left or right of the person traveling to liverpool##3
3. the person watching spy movies is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |    2     |
| City    | paris | liverpool    |
| Cigar         | fonseca        | bluemaster |
| Flower         | bellflower          | balloon-flower     |
| Movie-Genre   | spy        | zombie     |

 